1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
This position does not exist. I just lost $40 to it.
这个仓位不存在。我为它亏了 40 美元。

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:09,000
My bot placed a sell to close a long.
我的机器人下了一个卖单，本意是平掉一个多单。

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:14,000
Same account. Same second.
同一账户，同一秒钟。

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:19,000
The long closed. The sell also opened a new short.
多单平掉了。但那个卖单同时开了一个新的空单。

5
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Coinbase's API doesn't know a "close" is a close.
Coinbase 的 API 不知道"平仓"是平仓。

6
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Here's what the bot sent — no reduce_only, no close endpoint.
机器人发出去是这样的 —— 没 reduce_only，也没调专用接口。

7
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,000
Unless you set reduce_only, or hit a special endpoint. My bot did neither.
除非你设 reduce_only，或调用专用接口。我的机器人两样都没做。

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:40,000
So stop-loss fired. The long closed at a loss. And the ghost short kept bleeding.
止损触发。多单以亏损平掉。那个幽灵空单继续流血。

9
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:43,000
I then spent 20 hours blaming the wrong things.
接下来 20 小时，我一直在怪错对象。
